<div id="footer-block3" class="footer-block">
<div class="ftr-indent">
<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<p>HSHV's mission is to support the loving, responsible care of all animals in our community by:</p>
<ul>
<li>Ensuring proper, nurturing care for the animals in our shelter</li>
<li>Placing all adoptable animals in loving homes</li>
<li>Reducing pet over-population</li>
<li>Caring for the physical well-being of animals in our community</li>
<li>Providing education and outreach to the community</li>
<li>Stopping animal cruelty</li>
</ul>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
